<p><strong>编号：86</strong></p>
<p><strong>佛山禅城公安</strong><strong>“破小案”战斗集体</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201012/ece012d36ff8440a97b6f55bccd75866.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
